The President of Black First Land First (BLF), Andile Mngxitama, has been banned from twitter since last year. BLF notes the existence of multiple twitter accounts under his name. These are all fake. Mngxitama has not yet decided to return to Twitter and has been off that platform for a year now. Issued by Black First Land First, National Coordinating Committee of (BLF NCC)
